data.description: Situated in a desirable neighborhood in Killeen, this home offers both tranquility and convenience. Nearby parks, schools, and shopping centers make everyday living a breeze. Plus, it's just a short drive to Fort Hood, making it an excellent choice for military families! This well maintained property combines modern amenities with timeless charm, creating an inviting and comfortable living space for you and your family! And, as an added bonus, the seller is generously offering a $1500 flooring concession to ensure your new space feels just right.
